\p{The main contribution of this PR is [a
proof](Synthetic.Categories.HomFamilies) that a [simplicial
type](stt-00AC) is a precategory iff the family #{\Hom(x,-)} is
covariant for each #{x} - an important prerequisite for the Yoneda
lemma. We also add:}

\ul{
\li{The [functoriality of covariant transport](stt-00DQ)}
\li{[Dependent composition](stt-00DP) in inner families}
\li{[An adjunction](stt-00D5) between the [directed join](stt-00CW) and the
[(co)slice type](stt-00C4).}
\li{The definition and characterisation of [the walking homotopy](stt-00DK)}
  \li{The definition of the [pushout join](stt-00DE) and
  [pullback slice](stt-00DF)}
}

